## File Locations

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `.taskmaster/config.json` | AI provider configuration |
| `.taskmaster/docs/prd.txt` | Product requirements document |
| `.taskmaster/tasks/tasks.json` | Generated task hierarchy |
| `.taskmaster/reports/task-complexity-report.json` | Complexity analysis |
| `tasks/[id]/*` | Individual task files (after generate) |

---

## Workflow Summary

```
1. Configure providers → config.json
2. Write/refine PRD → prd.txt
3. Parse PRD → tasks.json
4. Analyze complexity → complexity report
5. Iterate (expand or modify PRD) until 90% under threshold
6. Execute tasks in order (next → implement → complete → repeat)
```
